# Dotfiles/Dotfolders 일괄 제외 (AI도구, IDE, 빌드캐시, 환경변수 등 한번에 처리)
.*
!.gitignore
!.env.example
!.github/
!.gitkeep

# 보안
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
credentials.json
service-account*.json

# AI instruction files (non-dot)
*.md
!README.md

# 빌드/의존성
node_modules/
dist/
out/
build/
target/

# DB
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
data/
